  "rationale": "The page follows the brief's argument arc: reveal \u2192 what shipped \u2192 who believes \u2192 the ask. The hero reuses hero-photo-overlay \u2014 the sanctioned display-title-over-media treatment lets the 'Breeze Agents are here.' claim sit on the full-bleed office photo (the only legal text-on-media). What-shipped renders the four launch agents as ONE cards run of four parallel cells (adapt, on-grid, even columns \u2014 disciplined SaaS alignment, offGridExpansion notwithstanding), each bound to its real product icon so the media never carries the argument alone. The beta-proof band is a quiet panel-toned stat-block (12,000+ / 135+ / 4) doing belief transfer before conversion. A single strong verbatim quote beats the seed's tabbed multi-case device, so testimonial is adapted to one quote block. Close reuses closing-cta-dark on the deep-teal inverse surface (dark reserved for the closing sequence per never-dark-mid-page), heading + one support line + primary/quiet action pair. No footer (renderer appends chrome). All headings sentence case, serif display over sans body, single action-orange accent confined to controls, no exclamation marks."
